                            "title": "Educational Media as Foundations of Curriculum",
                            "description": "Provides a historically-grounded treatment of the constructive role of technologies in the transmission and production of cultural knowledge and understanding. Students develop a grasp of the ways in which technologies have mediated and transformed the nature of knowledge, the knower, and processes of coming to know.",
                            "credits": "4",
